Package com.myPack

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AI
    This is for computer to play smart.
    AiHelpSheet
    This class is to help the computer to play and find houses and keep their data.
    AiRotationHelp
    This is a class to help the computer to find the best rotation possible to get the best result.
    AiRotationSheet
    This class is for keeping the changes in rotation to keep their score and their rotation situation.
    Ball
    This class is a player single ball that he or she will put it on the board.
    Board
    this is a superclass for the Print and Check classes and it changes the parts to a 6 * 6 2D array.
    CheckTheBoard
    This class is for checking the board.
    Computer
    This is the computer program for playing in a single mode.
    PartOfBoard
    This class is one part of the 4 parts of the main board.
    Pentago
    This is the main class of the project.
    PlayOnBoard
    This class is a subclass of the Board class.
    Print
    This class is for printing the output in cmd and it only has one method.
    RunTest
    This is just a test for out program.
